high_descs: Move to the table to the left of you
Pick up a ladle from the table
Move to the sink to the right of you
Place the ladle in the sink and run water for a moment before picking it up and turning off the water
Move to the table behind you
Place the ladle on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ladle on the table in front of the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the dining table.
Grab the ladle from the dining table.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the ladle in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to the left side of the dining table.
Put the ladle back on the table, in front of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned ladle on a dining table.

high_descs: Go to the brown table on the left.
Pick up the metal ladle resting on the green sponge on the table.
Turn right to go to the sink on the right.
Place the ladle in the sink and wash with water, and take it out when done.
Turn around to go back to the wooden table.
Place the ladle resting on the front of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Wash the ladle and place it on the tomato.
